ronmental-infographic/#comments" rel="comment"> 17 </a> </span></div> </header><div class="post_share rail"><div class="large-buttons"><div class="wdt_button"><iframe id="tweet_frame_599673" name="tweet_frame_599673" class="twitter-share-button" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" role="presentation" scrolling="no" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2F2011%2F04%2F26%2Fscooters-environmental-infographic%2F&amp;via=mashabletech%20%40mashable&amp;text=How%20Scooters%20Are%20Saving%20the%20Planet%20%5BINFOGRAPHIC%5D&amp;count=vertical" width="55" height="63"></iframe></div><div class="wdt_button wdt_fb"><fb:like href="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" layout="box_count"></fb:like></div><div class="wdt_button"><div id="su_v_599673"></div></div><div class="wdt_button"><a class="chicklet block st_email" data-uri="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" data-title="How Scooters Are Saving the Planet [INFOGRAPHIC]" href="javascript:">email</a></div><div class="wdt_button"><a class="chicklet block st_sharethis" data-uri="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" data-title="How Scooters Are Saving the Planet [INFOGRAPHIC]" href="javascript:">share</a></div></div><div class="small-buttons" style="display:none"><div class="wdt_button_min"><iframe id="tweet_frame_599673" name="tweet_frame_599673" class="twitter-share-button" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" role="presentation" scrolling="no" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2F2011%2F04%2F26%2Fscooters-environmental-infographic%2F&amp;via=mashabletech%20%40mashable&amp;text=How%20Scooters%20Are%20Saving%20the%20Planet%20%5BINFOGRAPHIC%5D&amp;count=horizontal" width="110" height="20"></iframe></div><div class="wdt_button_min"><fb:like href="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" layout="button_count"></fb:like></div><div class="wdt_button_min"><div id="su_h_599673" style="width:75px;height:22px;"></div></div><div class="wdt_button_min"><a class="chicklet block st_email" data-uri="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" data-title="How Scooters Are Saving the Planet [INFOGRAPHIC]" href="javascript:">email</a></div><div class="wdt_button_min"><a class="chicklet block st_sharethis" data-uri="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" data-title="How Scooters Are Saving the Planet [INFOGRAPHIC]" href="javascript:">share</a></div></div></div><div class="description"><div class="post-fb-like"> <fb:like href="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" send="true" width="625" height="61"></fb:like></div><p><img src="http://7.mshcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/scooter-environment.jpg" alt="" title="scooter-environment" width="225" height="141" class="alignright size-full wp-image-599709" />Need to justify that gratuitous Vespa purchase? According to research from the Environmental Protection Agency, AAA and other sources, using scooters &#8212; even occasionally &#8212; can help reduce carbon emissions, save gasoline and increase worker productivity by stunning amounts.</p><p>For example, if U.S. cities were made more scooter friendly, we could save almost 4 billion gallons of gas annually by 2020 &#8212; and that means decreasing our dependence on foreign oil to $21.4 billion per year. The savings would also include 77.3 billion pounds of CO2 emissions each year.</p><p>The research was compiled into a friendly graphical presentation by the folks at <a href="http://www.vespausa.com/" target="_blank">VespaUSA</a> (who clearly have an interest in promoting the economic and ecological benefits of the scooter) and <a href="http://mashable.com/tag/mint/">Mint.com</a>, Intuit&#8217;s personal finance app for consumers.</p><p><em>Click image to see the larger version.</em></p><p><center><a href="http://8.mshcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/scooter-infographic.png"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/scooter-infographic-sm.jpg" alt="" title="scooter-infographic-sm" width="640" height="1536" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-599701" /></a></p><p></center></p><p><em>Lead image courtesy of Flickr, <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/42424413@N06/4225335724/in/photostream/" target="_blank">lord enfield</a></em></p></div><div class="post-actions"> <a class="print_story" href="javascript:window.print();">Print Story</a> <a class="chicklet st_email" data-uri="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/" data-title="How Scooters Are Saving the Planet [INFOGRAPHIC]" href="#">Email Story</a></div><footer class="post_footer clearfix"><h6>Topics to follow</h6><ul id="post-follow-topics" class="topics_list"><li> <a href="/follow/topics/mint"><img src="http://api.freebase.com/api/trans/image_thumb/en/mint_com?maxwidth=32&maxheight=32&mode=fillcrop" alt="Mint" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/mint">Mint</a> 57 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/mint/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/infographics"><img src="http://api.freebase.com/api/trans/image_thumb/en/information_graphics?maxwidth=32&maxheight=32&mode=fillcrop" alt="Infographics" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/infographics">Infographics</a> 218 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/infographics/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/electric-cars"><img src="http://api.freebase.com/api/trans/image_thumb/en/electric_car?maxwidth=32&maxheight=32&mode=fillcrop" alt="Electric cars" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/electric-cars">Electric cars</a> 12 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/electric-cars/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/mint.com"><img src="http://cache.daylife.com/imageserve/04pdf8M85t68B/32x32.jpg" alt="Mint.com" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/mint.com">Mint.com</a> 6 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/mint.com/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/environment"><img src="http://api.freebase.com/api/trans/image_thumb/en/natural_environment?maxwidth=32&maxheight=32&mode=fillcrop" alt="Environment" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/environment">Environment</a> 18 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/environment/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/green"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/follow/uploads/topic/image/3a/68/bd/6f/49/08/thumb_green-1668522e34.jpeg" alt="Green" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/green">Green</a> 25 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/green/follow">Follow</a></li></ul><ul id="post-follow-topics-more" class="topics_list"><li> <a href="/follow/topics/scooter"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/follow/images/default_topic_32x32.png" alt="Scooter" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/scooter">Scooter</a> 0 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/scooter/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/scooters"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/follow/images/default_topic_32x32.png" alt="Scooters" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/scooters">Scooters</a> 0 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/scooters/follow">Follow</a></li><li> <a href="/follow/topics/vespa"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/follow/images/default_topic_32x32.png" alt="Vespa" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/vespa">Vespa</a> 0 fo