/thumb_matthew-duff-ffe29d11bd.jpg' /> </a></div><span class='author-link'><a href='/follow/people/4db749745198407d50000020/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Matthew Duff</a></span> <a href="/follow/people/4db749745198407d50000020/follow/" class="follow_button" data-badges="1" data-followers="0">Follow</a></div><div class="comment-body"><p>I drove a Vespa to/from work/school for four years. It was the best form of transportation. There were about three months where I couldn&#8217;t use it, but it was heaven during all the other months. I only stopped using it because I now work too far away to use the Vespa.</p><p>My monthly payment was $100/month and full coverage insurance was $19/month. I spent about $12-$16 in gas a month. It was incredible. I bought it for $4200 and sold it five years later for $1500 (I had laid it down and gotten $2000 insurance claim from it). I also rented it out for a year and made $700 doing that.</p><p>I ended up making money on it. It was amazing. And it was incredibly convenient for parking. I would buy another one in a heart beat. I am going to get the 250cc one of these days.</p></div><div class="comment-actions"> <a href="http://mashable.com/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/#comment-17279547" class="comment-timestamp"><time datetime="Tue, 26 Apr 2011 18:42:48 -0400">April 26, 2011 18:42:48</time> </a> <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/04/26/scooters-environmental-infographic/?replytocom=17279547#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-17279547", "17279547", "respond", "599673")'>Reply</a> <a href="/follow/comments/4db74a6c51984012620031b2/vote?v=1" class='vote vote-up ' data-remote="" data-method="PUT">0</a> <a href="/follow/comments/4db74a6c51984012620031b2/flag" class="flag ">Flag this comment</a></div></div></li><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-17279637"><hr /><div id="comment-17279637" class="comment-wrapper "><div class="comment-author vcard"><div c